                #### INSTALLATION ####

plumetrack is distributed using Python's setuptools 
utility. Once you have installed the dependencies, running:
  
   python setup.py build
   python setup.py install

will install the plumetrack program. Note that you may need
administrative privilidges for the install command. For full
installation instructions, please see the 
docs/build/html/installation.html document.



                   #### USAGE ####

Full usage instructions for plumetrack can be found in the 
html documentation which can be found in the docs/build/html
folder of this distribution.



